uk.ac.kent.models.records

Class PersonalDetailsRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.kent.models.records.BaseRecord
      • uk.ac.kent.models.records.PersonalDetailsRecord

  • @Entity
public final class PersonalDetailsRecord
extends BaseRecord
    A BaseRecord of an Employee's personal details. This is how the system stores personal info about all Employees - not in the Employee class but rather in a PersonalDetailsRecord.

    This class makes use of (is associated with) Address and Relative.

    Author:
    norbert
